---
title: Minced Turkey Navarin Stew with Creamy Mashed Potatoes
description: This French-inspired turkey stew is packed with the aromatic trifecta of onions, celery and carrots.  Ground turkey and creamy mashed potatoes make it the perfect dish to satisfy your comfort food craving.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-navarin-de-dinde-7794df88.jpg
